00:21:42.882 --> 00:21:44.212
Especially with Mom and Dad to consider.

00:21:45.642 --> 00:21:49.252
But it got to the point where his divorce didn't matter.

00:21:49.952 --> 00:21:51.682
That's how much I fell for Seong Jae.

00:21:52.722 --> 00:21:53.752
Su Bin.

00:21:55.992 --> 00:21:57.122
It's not just about the divorce.

00:21:58.222 --> 00:21:59.862
What do you mean, it's not just about the divorce?

00:22:00.492 --> 00:22:01.962
There's a whole world you don't know about.

00:22:02.732 --> 00:22:05.432
So, until Seong Jae sorts this out and I give you my permission,

00:22:05.902 --> 00:22:07.502
