I've come for your answer, Father.

00:55:24.462 --> 00:55:25.532
What if the answer is no?

00:55:27.662 --> 00:55:28.872
I'll resign.

00:55:33.942 --> 00:55:34.972
You'll resign?

00:55:36.242 --> 00:55:39.542
I'll return all the company stock you gave me.

00:55:41.712 --> 00:55:43.052
And to think you said you were just dating.

00:55:43.452 --> 00:55:45.282
You're willing to give up everything and walk out?

00:55:45.982 --> 00:55:47.922
I'm saying I'll leave your company.

00:55:49.522 --> 00:55:51.662
I'll focus on growing Next Labs,

00:55:51.762 --> 00:55:53.622
the company I started with the money from Grandpa.

00:55:54.122 --> 00:55:55.662
Besides, I'm more interested in investing.

00:55:58.602 --> 00:56:03.332
So now that you have your own money, you think you can do as you please?

00:56:03.932 --> 00:56:04.942
No.

00:56:05.472 --> 00:56:08.612
I'm saying you can't control me with your money anymore.

00:56:13.982 --> 00:56:15.282
This isn't about marriage, is it?

00:56:16.782 --> 00:56:18.552
Right. We're just dating.

00:56:19.682 --> 00:56:20.722
For now.

00:56:21.792 --> 00:56:22.952
Fine. Have it your way.

00:56:25.292 --> 00:56:29.432
If your relationship with her hurts the company or our family,

00:56:29.492 --> 00:56:32.132
then it's over. Mark my words.

00:56:33.662 --> 00:56:34.702
Understood.

00:56:39.542 --> 00:56:41.472
I'm dying to see Su Bin.

00:56:52.552 --> 00:56:55.992
If I leave all this food out, he'll help himself, I'm sure.

00:56:56.652 --> 00:56:57.652
All set.

00:57:02.892 --> 00:57:03.892
Right.

00:57:06.132 --> 00:57:07.132
What?

00:57:09.602 --> 00:57:10.702
Cheol Min.

00:57:11.002 --> 00:57:13.242
Could you sort the meeting minutes for me?

00:57:13.842 --> 00:57:14.842
Sure.

00:57:28.392 --> 00:57:30.152
I was just about to head out. What's up?

00:57:32.022 --> 00:57:33.622
Can we talk for a minute?

00:57:36.392 --> 00:57:38.262
But I really have to get going right now.

00:57:38.562 --> 00:57:41.532
- I just came back to get my phone. - I make you uncomfortable, right?

00:57:43.332 --> 00:57:46.102
Showing up right after your surgery when you couldn't even move,

00:57:47.242 --> 00:57:48.772
hanging around your hospital room,

00:57:50.572 --> 00:57:52.342
telling you I can't give up on you,

00:57:53.812 --> 00:57:54.882
and now...

00:57:55.982 --> 00:57:57.482
asking you to join my company.

00:58:01.122 --> 00:58:04.192
Why are you saying all this all of a sudden?

00:58:04.722 --> 00:58:06.792
There's something I've been meaning to tell you,

00:58:08.432 --> 00:58:09.532
and I'm going to say it now.

00:58:14.162 --> 00:58:15.732
I've been a real jerk.

00:58:19.202 --> 00:58:20.372
Eun Oh, I...

00:58:21.672 --> 00:58:23.912
When I decided to marry Jung Bo A,

00:58:25.582 --> 00:58:28.052
I truly thought it was a win-win marriage.

00:58:30.182 --> 00:58:32.252
She had what I lacked,

00:58:33.652 --> 00:58:35.092
and she needed me.

00:58:37.152 --> 00:58:40.822
So I truly believed I wasn't doing anything wrong.

00:58:46.132 --> 00:58:47.802
I know that's what you thought.

00:58:49.202 --> 00:58:50.202
But...

00:58:50.732 --> 00:58:53.842
- why are you saying this now? - But I overlooked something.

00:58:56.172 --> 00:58:57.372
The fact that Jung Bo A was still...

00:58:58.942 --> 00:59:00.782
in love with another man.

00:59:04.212 --> 00:59:05.852
And even though I knew all that,

00:59:07.552 --> 00:59:09.022
I was still going to marry her.

00:59:11.522 --> 00:59:13.292
A real jerk who was just in it for the money.

00:59:14.962 --> 00:59:15.962
That was me.

00:59:20.562 --> 00:59:22.002
And you're only just now realising that?

00:59:22.172 --> 00:59:24.232
So I can only imagine how much you must've despised me.

00:59:26.072 --> 00:59:27.972
And yet, I showed up at your cafe...

00:59:27.972 --> 00:59:30.242
trying to come back and bothering you.

00:59:32.742 --> 00:59:33.742
In the process...

00:59:36.212 --> 00:59:37.512
I ended up falling for you.

00:59:44.862 --> 00:59:45.922
As for that,

00:59:47.022 --> 00:59:49.262
I already gave you my answer back then.

00:59:50.832 --> 00:59:52.332
You're just pathetic.

00:59:52.832 --> 00:59:54.702
What's the point of you liking me now?

00:59:55.232 --> 00:59:58.172
It's all pointless now. That kind of person...

00:59:58.872 --> 00:59:59.902
I can't stand them.

00:59:59.902 --> 01:00:02.212
Someone who would marry without love for money...

01:00:02.272 --> 01:00:04.072
I despise people like that.

01:00:07.282 --> 01:00:08.312
You did.

01:00:10.012 --> 01:00:12.922
That our values are too different,

01:00:13.722 --> 01:00:15.222
so we're a terrible match.

01:00:17.422 --> 01:00:19.792
I told you we were beyond repair.

01:00:21.992 --> 01:00:23.032
But...

01:00:26.462 --> 01:00:27.462
Eun Oh.

01:00:31.502 --> 01:00:32.942
I really think...

01:00:34.912 --> 01:00:36.312
you're the only one for me, for as long as I live.

01:00:39.682 --> 01:00:41.812
How can I earn your forgiveness?

01:00:45.422 --> 01:00:46.552
Can you please tell me?

01:00:48.592 --> 01:00:49.592
What I have to do...

01:00:51.692 --> 01:00:53.322
to earn your forgiveness.

01:00:59.132 --> 01:01:01.032
Watching you go through surgery this time...

01:01:03.172 --> 01:01:04.532
made me realise it for sure.

01:01:08.242 --> 01:01:09.542
I just can't let you go.

01:01:15.182 --> 01:01:17.112
You're so shameless.

01:01:18.852 --> 01:01:20.552
After getting your way with everything,

01:01:21.182 --> 01:01:23.122
now you're trying to get your way with me too.

01:01:24.962 --> 01:01:26.162
The reasons this won't work between us...

01:01:27.162 --> 01:01:28.632
I've explained them more than enough.

01:01:31.902 --> 01:01:32.962
I'm sorry.

01:01:35.672 --> 01:01:36.732
I really am.

01:01:40.042 --> 01:01:41.142
I'm truly sorry.

01:01:46.282 --> 01:01:47.742
I want you to forgive me.

01:01:59.892 --> 01:02:01.162
You said it yourself, right?

01:02:03.432 --> 01:02:06.002
"I'm going to do everything I can for you."

01:02:07.102 --> 01:02:08.272
"And you do whatever you want."

01:02:11.132 --> 01:02:12.302
Fine, let's do that.

01:02:14.502 --> 01:02:15.512
Because I'm...

01:02:16.372 --> 01:02:17.972
going to do exactly what I want, too.

01:02:22.412 --> 01:02:23.512
I have to be somewhere.

01:02:25.082 --> 01:02:26.082
Right.

01:02:26.822 --> 01:02:27.822
You...

01:02:28.752 --> 01:02:29.822
You just told me...

01:02:30.422 --> 01:02:31.892
to do whatever I want, didn't you?

01:02:33.222 --> 01:02:34.592
Then that's exactly what I'll do.

01:02:51.912 --> 01:02:52.912
What?

01:02:55.952 --> 01:02:56.952
What a klutz.

01:02:57.882 --> 01:02:59.122
Especially when it's so cold out.

01:03:02.292 --> 01:03:04.152
What? Did she grab a cab already?

01:03:08.392 --> 01:03:09.992
She's taking the bus?

01:03:13.902 --> 01:03:15.172
Eun Oh, you dropped this...

01:03:29.352 --> 01:03:30.952
What? Dad!

01:03:32.952 --> 01:03:33.982
Dad?

01:03:34.582 --> 01:03:37.292
- Mr. Early, you're his dad? - What?

01:03:39.262 --> 01:03:40.822
Wait, "Mr. Early?"

01:03:41.932 --> 01:03:45.732
Hold on, you know my father?

01:04:30.512 --> 01:04:32.782
(Our Golden Days)

01:04:33.442 --> 01:04:34.442
I love you.

01:04:34.512 --> 01:04:37.882
Marriage? A hundred days turn into a year, then two years.

01:04:37.952 --> 01:04:39.552
And who knows? We might actually get married.

01:04:39.652 --> 01:04:43.792
- Actually, I met that young lady. - She's a feisty one, isn't she?

01:04:43.992 --> 01:04:46.592
Why should I have to tell you about my friends?

01:04:46.662 --> 01:04:48.022
Come out, you punk.

01:04:48.292 --> 01:04:52.502
- You have a crush on her, right? - Dad!

01:04:52.562 --> 01:04:55.032
Honey, you really get a kick out of teasing Ji Hyuk.

01:04:55.102 --> 01:04:57.602
- You got this, right? - You got this, too, right?

01:04:57.672 --> 01:04:59.902
I'm the architect of this project.

01:05:00.402 --> 01:05:02.142
There's someone I want to go see...